Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild

Record Class Guild

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild.Guild
Record Components:
id - The id of the guild
name - The name of the guild
icon - The icon hash of the guild
iconHash - The icon hash of the guild (included with template object)
splash - The splash hash of the guild
discoverySplash - The discovery splash hash of the guild
isOwner - Whether the user is the owner of the guild
owner - The owner of the guild
permissions - The total permissions of the user in the guild (excludes overwrites)
afkChannel - The afk channel of the guild
afkTimeout - The afk timeout of the guild
isWidgetEnabled - Whether the widget is enabled for the guild
widgetChannel - The widget channel of the guild
verificationLevel - The verification level of the guild
defaultMessageNotificationLevel - The default message notification level of the guild
explicitContentFilterLevel - The explicit content filter level of the guild
roles - The roles of the guild
emojis - The emojis of the guild
features - The features of the guild
mfaLevel - The mfa level of the guild
applicationId - The application id of the guild
systemChannel - The system channel of the guild
maxPresences - The maximum presences of the guild
maxMembers - The maximum members of the guild
vanityUrlCode - The vanity url code of the guild
description - The description of the guild
banner - The banner hash of the guild
premiumTier - The premium tier of the guild
premiumSubscriptionCount - The premium subscription count of the guild
preferredLocale - The preferred locale of the guild
publicUpdatesChannel - The public updates channel of the guild
maxVideoChannelUsers - The maximum video channel users of the guild
approximateMemberCount - The approximate member count of the guild
approximatePresenceCount - The approximate presence count of the guild
welcomeScreen - The welcome screen of the guild
stickers - The stickers of the guild
premiumProgressBarEnabled - Whether the premium progress bar is enabled for the guild
